id":289142,"uid":90827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:16:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見過啲main con 搵大學寫報告既field work<br />\n<br />\n啲 PhD 學生爭住做，屌那星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恕我無知,何謂main con"},{"pid":"041e8e04fd53cddc4de6cbfda427a1cb5ba1dc11","tid":289142,"uid":30972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:24:39.000Z","msg":"巴打 係香港讀envir冇你諗得咁理想 要真係接觸動物 做考驗不如讀bio啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d1510255d47de0f9348759afce588c3d04ff2f","tid":289142,"uid":90827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打 係香港讀envir冇你諗得咁理想 要真係接觸動物 做考驗不如讀bio啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可惜ou冇淨bio讀<br />\n一係就applied science(chem &amp; bio)<br />\n但我又唔中意chem<br />\n不過d科野都同environment好相似"},{"pid":"582cdfeb8a13fdd6bc3f19af92a06de2a5aae40e","tid":289142,"uid":30972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:41:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打 係香港讀envir冇你諗得咁理想 要真係接觸動物 做考驗不如讀bio啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可惜ou冇淨bio讀<br />\n一係就applied science(chem &amp; bio)<br />\n但我又唔中意chem<br />\n不過d科野都同environment好相似</blockquote><br />\n因為envir最最最主要係讀air noise water waste soil(都少啲) 關考察事我諗得ecology 同EIA 但香港係ecology同EIA方面都唔會教太多啲生物考察相關嘅野 <br />\n<br />\n除非巴打你好心機讀上phd 否則真係好難做到同生物考察有關嘅工<br />\n<br />\n上面只係個人意見同觀點 可能有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32257f8bb9fc36fec547e078053a3441a859a104","tid":289142,"uid":17418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:46:48.000Z","msg":"樓主讀錯科/生錯地方<br />\n<br />\n利申同行"},{"pid":"b4f30c67c606bcf5e5f8efd05563da8096179a96","tid":289142,"uid":90827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:56:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783d0b0966057c208df5a1e2cb5e22549007f796","tid":289142,"uid":90827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主讀錯科/生錯地方<br />\n<br />\n利申同行</blockquote><br />\n請問你做緊咩工種"},{"pid":"1e3408a997aab27433590e9fd66ea1d9751f339d","tid":289142,"uid":90827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:06:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跟porf做RA<br />\n做得掂就跟佢讀上去<br />\n<br />\n建議樓主主動啲搵老細，唔好怕羞，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人生只有一次，放膽去做，俾心機</blockquote><br />\n唔好意思, 我又要問下咩係ra"},{"pid":"574d55854a795d1ada724d978a47f9b6d044ad44","tid":289142,"uid":21699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:08:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跟porf做RA<br />\n做得掂就跟佢讀上去<br />\n<br />\n建議樓主主動啲搵老細，唔好怕羞，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人生只有一次，放膽去做，俾心機</blockquote><br />\n唔好意思, 我又要問下咩係ra</blockquote><br />\nResearch assistant<br />\n通常想入學術界呢行，唔係讀master/mphil/phd，就係做RA"},{"pid":"64fb87a405958d01fa5bd6215e1c9d9ab5ba1081","tid":289142,"uid":90827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:09:44.000Z","msg":"請問你地建議我再讀上去<br />\n係要讀到碩士定博士<br />\n同埋讀咩科<br />\n先至做到field work"},{"pid":"a8d6daf9359e6efebc40ca76af5003be13531498","tid":289142,"uid":18624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T16:57:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問你地建議我再讀上去<br />\n係要讀到碩士定博士<br />\n同埋讀咩科<br />\n先至做到field work</blockquote><br />\necology/biology/EIA 相關科目好啲<br />\n係香港真係好難搞<br />\n去外國讀會好好多"},{"pid":"99c1503717cf59ee9796caa02265a594a0c07d44","tid":289142,"uid":18666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:02:23.000Z","msg":"有無eb巴打可以分享吓有咩工做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}